:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:356:"Today we are happy to announce a few WPML compatible themes. The themes are Zerif PRO, WPRentals, Trendz, Accounting, Shoped. If you want to review the entire multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here: Multilingual Ready Themes Multilingual Ready Plugins Also, if you’re a theme or a plugin author and you [&#8230;]";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:15:"Mohamed Khafaja";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:5037:"<p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-954065" src="https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/WPML-Compatible-themes-300x84.png" alt="WPML Compatible themes" width="450" height="126" srcset="https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/WPML-Compatible-themes-300x84.png 300w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/WPML-Compatible-themes-150x42.png 150w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/WPML-Compatible-themes.png 568w" sizes="(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px" /></p>\n<p>Today we are happy to announce a few WPML compatible themes.</p>\n<p>The themes are Zerif<a href="http://themeisle.com/themes/zerif-pro-one-page-wordpress-theme/"> PRO</a>, <a href="https://themeforest.net/item/wp-rentals-booking-accommodation-wordpress-theme/12921802">WPRentals</a>, <a href="https://themeforest.net/item/trendz-woocommerce-shopping-wordpress-theme/14907135">Trendz</a>, <a href="https://themeforest.net/item/accounting-wp-business-theme-for-accountants/11444926">Accounting</a>,<a href="https://themeforest.net/item/shoped-multipurpose-minimal-woocommerce-theme/14231820"> Shoped</a>.</p>\n<p>If you want to review the entire multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href="https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/">Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a href="https://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if you’re a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, we welcome you and ready to help: You are welcome to contact us at <a href="https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/">go global program page</a>.</p>\n<p>In order to expedite the process we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with our <a href="https://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin Multilingual Ready.</p>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Zerif PRO</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Zerif PRO is a single-page parallax theme. It offers customizable content blocks and slide-in effects on the main page. The single-page structure makes this responsive WordPress theme perfect for website owners who are not planning to have a lot of content on their sites, and want to focus on generating contacts and leads for their businesses.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeisle.com/themes/zerif-pro-one-page-wordpress-theme/">Purchase Zerif PRO</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">WPRentals</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Ultimate WordPress Theme created by WP Estate for accommodation booking. WP Rentals is clean, flexible, fully responsive and retina Ready. Its smart settings allows you to build outstanding renting websites easy and fast.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://themeforest.net/item/wp-rentals-booking-accommodation-wordpress-theme/12921802">Purchase WPRentals</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Trendz</h2>\n<blockquote><p>WooCommerce WordPress Theme.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://themeforest.net/item/trendz-woocommerce-shopping-wordpress-theme/14907135">Purchase Trendz</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Accounting</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Accounting theme is a WordPress business theme.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://themeforest.net/item/accounting-wp-business-theme-for-accountants/11444926">Purchase Accounting</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Shoped</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Shoped is a HTML5/CSS3/Bootstrap optimized responsive, minimal theme perfect for multi-purpose Commerce website.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://themeforest.net/item/shoped-multipurpose-minimal-woocommerce-theme/14231820">Purchase Shoped</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=oxKPgq7QrRA:GtKHHXZU-Zg:D7DqB2pKExk"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=oxKPgq7QrRA:GtKHHXZU-Zg:D7DqB2pKExk" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=oxKPgq7QrRA:GtKHHXZU-Zg:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=oxKPgq7QrRA:GtKHHXZU-Zg:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=oxKPgq7QrRA:GtKHHXZU-Zg:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=oxKPgq7QrRA:GtKHHXZU-Zg:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a>\n</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpml/~4/oxKPgq7QrRA" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s: