"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:3003:"<p>Today we are happy to announce and present SmartMATE WordPress Connect, the recent integration between <a href="https://wpml.org">WPML</a> and <a href="http://www.capitatranslationinterpreting.com/">Capita</a>, a leading translation service.</p>\n<p><img class="size-medium wp-image-948139 aligncenter" src="https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/wpmlCapita-1-300x118.png" alt="wpml+Capita" width="300" height="118" srcset="https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/wpmlCapita-1-300x118.png 300w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/wpmlCapita-1-150x59.png 150w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/wpmlCapita-1.png 347w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">Capita Translation and Interpreting (Capita TI) is a leading provider of language services to both public and private organisations. They offer a wide range of professional translation and interpreting services, including website localisation, face-to-face interpreting, voiceover and subtitling, and multilingual SEO, in over 180 languages.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">They can offer extensive experience and resources, as well as reliable end-to-end solutions to help businesses and community groups translate everything, from websites and important documentation, to software and digital files, so that internal stakeholders and customers alike can understand the information they require, no matter what language they speak.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">Their  processes and capabilities are demonstrated by their ISO accreditations in information security; quality of management systems; and environmental management.</p>\n<p>Now, with SmartMATE WordPress Connect you will enjoy:</p>\n<p>·        Seamless system integration</p>\n<p>·        Quick and secure set-up process</p>\n<p>·        Eliminate manual copy/paste tasks</p>\n<p>·        Full user control and visibility over translation projects</p>\n<p>·        Cost and time savings achieved through Capita&#8217;s innovative Language Technology</p>\n<p>To learn more about the new SmartMATE WordPress Connect, please visit: <a href="https://wpml.org/translation-service/capita/">https://wpml.org/translation-service/capita/</a></p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=4_ZJ-rfxa-M:qusn5Xxpiv0:D7DqB2pKExk"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=4_ZJ-rfxa-M:qusn5Xxpiv0:D7DqB2pKExk" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=4_ZJ-rfxa-M:qusn5Xxpiv0:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=4_ZJ-rfxa-M:qusn5Xxpiv0:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=4_ZJ-rfxa-M:qusn5Xxpiv0:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=4_ZJ-rfxa-M:qusn5Xxpiv0:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a>\n</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpml/~4/4_ZJ-rfxa-M" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:81:"https://wpml.org/2016/07/wpml-capita-integrates-smartmate-wordpress-connect/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:42:"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0";a:1:{s:8:"origLink";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:76:"https://wpml.org/2016/07/wpml-capita-integrates-smartmate-wordpress-connect/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:45:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:6:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Compatible Plugins – Jul 2016";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:51:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/wpml/~3/Yq5gT5_tJ5Q/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:62:"https://wpml.org/2016/07/compatible-plugins-jul-2016/#comments";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Tue, 05 Jul 2016 11:28:16 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:13:"Announcements";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:13:"Compatibility";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:26:"https://wpml.org/?p=941331";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:347:"Today we are happy to announce a few WPML compatible plugins. The plugins are, XML Sitemap &#38; Google News feeds ,PiwigoPress, VR Calendar Pro, Buttons Shortcode and Widget, WP All Export, Super Store Finder, Widgetize Pages Light. If you want to review the entire multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view [&#8230;]";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:15:"Mohamed Khafaja";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:5727:"<p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-941424" src="https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Compatible-Plugins-Header-300x90.png" alt="Compatible Plugins-Header" width="400" height="121" srcset="https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Compatible-Plugins-Header-300x90.png 300w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Compatible-Plugins-Header-150x45.png 150w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Compatible-Plugins-Header.png 680w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" /></p>\n<p>Today we are happy to announce a few WPML compatible plugins.</p>\n<p>The plugins are, <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/xml-sitemap-feed/">XML Sitemap &amp; Google News feed</a>s ,<a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/piwigopress/">PiwigoPress</a>, <a href="https://codecanyon.net/item/vr-calendar-sync-pro-responsive-booking-plugin/13504469">VR Calendar Pro</a>, <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/buttons-shortcode-and-widget/">Buttons Shortcode and Widget</a>, <a href="http://www.wpallimport.com/export/">WP All Export</a>, <a href="https://codecanyon.net/item/super-store-finder-for-wordpress/11334595">Super Store Finder</a>, <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/widgetize-pages-light/">Widgetize Pages Light</a>.</p>\n<p>If you want to review the entire multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href="https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/">Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a href="https://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if you’re a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, we welcome you and ready to help: You are welcome to contact us at <a href="https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/">go global program page</a>.</p>\n<p>In order to expedite the process, we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with our <a href="https://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin Multilingual Ready.</p>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">XML Sitemap &amp; Google News feeds</h2>\n<blockquote><p>This plugin dynamically creates feeds that comply with the XML Sitemap and the Google News Sitemap protocol.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/xml-sitemap-feed/">Download XML Sitemap &amp; Google News feeds<br />\n</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">PiwigoPress</h2>\n<blockquote><p>From any open API Piwigo gallery, swiftly include your photos in Posts/Pages and/or add randomized thumbnails and menus in your sidebar.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/piwigopress/">Download PiwigoPress</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">VR Calendar Sync Pro</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/vr-calendar-sync-pro-responsive-booking-plugin/13504469">Purchase VR Calendar Sync Pro</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Buttons Shortcode and Widget</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Create buttons. Nice and easy interface. Insert anywhere in your site &#8211; page/post editor, sidebars, template files.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/buttons-shortcode-and-widget/">Download Buttons Shortcode and Widget</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">WP All Export</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Customize the layout of the export file. Edit your data and re-import it later with WP All Import.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://www.wpallimport.com/export/">Purchase WP All Export</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Super Store Finder</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Super Store Finder for WordPress is a fully-featured WordPress Plugin integrated with Google Maps API v3 that allows customers to locate your stores easily.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://codecanyon.net/item/super-store-finder-for-wordpress/11334595">Purchase Super Store Finder</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Widgetize Pages Light</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Drop widgets in page or post content area. Widgetized pages. Build your custom Responsive page layout in no time.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/widgetize-pages-light/">Download Widgetize Pages Light</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=Yq5gT5_tJ5Q:XuDaUfwf-oY:D7DqB2pKExk"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=Yq5gT5_tJ5Q:XuDaUfwf-oY:D7DqB2pKExk" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=Yq5gT5_tJ5Q:XuDaUfwf-oY:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=Yq5gT5_tJ5Q:XuDaUfwf-oY:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=Yq5gT5_tJ5Q:XuDaUfwf-oY:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=Yq5gT5_tJ5Q:XuDaUfwf-oY:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a>\n</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpml/~4/Yq5gT5_tJ5Q" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:58:"https://wpml.org/2016/07/compatible-plugins-jul-2016/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"1";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:42:"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0";a:1:{s:8:"origLink";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:53:"https://wpml.org/2016/07/compatible-plugins-jul-2016/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:42:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:6:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:44:"WPML and Transifex: New translation partners";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:51:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/wpml/~3/qyYpFLerx5s/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:73:"https://wpml.org/2016/07/wpml-transifex-new-translation-partners/#respond";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Fri, 01 Jul 2016 16:08:08 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:13:"Announcements";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:26:"https://wpml.org/?p=939658";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:419:"Today we are happy to announce the recent integration between WPML and Transifex, a leading translation management system. Transifex offers a robust, collaborative translation process where translators and reviewers can work together in a translation management system and leverage built-in features like Translation Memory and a Translation Glossary. Transifex also provides flexibility, enabling the use of [&#8230;]";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:13:"Ornela Flores";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:3126:"<p>Today we are happy to announce the recent integration between <a href="http://www.wpml.org">WPML</a> and <a href="http://www.transifex.com">Transifex</a>, a leading translation management system.</p>\n<p><img class="size-medium wp-image-939665 aligncenter" src="https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/wpmlTransifex-300x113.png" alt="wpml+Transifex" width="300" height="113" srcset="https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/wpmlTransifex-300x113.png 300w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/wpmlTransifex-150x57.png 150w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/wpmlTransifex.png 381w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></p>\n<p>Transifex offers a robust, collaborative translation process where translators and reviewers can work together in a translation management system and leverage built-in features like Translation Memory and a Translation Glossary. Transifex also provides flexibility, enabling the use of XLIFF files for translations, in addition to the new option of delivering translations back into the system thanks to WPML.</p>\n<p>“<em>Transifex’s mission is to make localization available to everyone</em>,&#8221; said Diego Búrigo Zacarão, head of Dev Ops and Architecture at Transifex, &#8220;<em>and our partnership with WPML demonstrates our commitment to support web publishers in order to make multilingual web experiences possible, in the way they want</em>.”</p>\n<p>Transifex serves a wide range of businesses, from startups to large companies, although most of their main clients would be considered mid-market companies.</p>\n<p>They  provide online support for all clients and dedicated Customer Success managers to their larger customers. They have staff in Europe and the U.S., and their Customer Success team is located across both continents.</p>\n<p>For WordPress site owners interested in learning more about how to implement a multilingual site, Transifex is sponsoring a joint webinar with WPML speaker Amit Kvint, Compatibility Team Leader, on Wednesday, July 12 at 9 am PDT. Interested participants can <a href="https://www.brighttalk.com/webcast/13375/210609">register here</a> to attend the in-depth online discussion.</p>\n<p>To learn more about the new WPML-Transifex solution, please visit <a href="https://wpml.org/translation-service/transifex/">https://wpml.org/translation-service/transifex/</a>.</p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=qyYpFLerx5s:gKTpfLbJFc4:D7DqB2pKExk"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=qyYpFLerx5s:gKTpfLbJFc4:D7DqB2pKExk" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=qyYpFLerx5s:gKTpfLbJFc4:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=qyYpFLerx5s:gKTpfLbJFc4:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=qyYpFLerx5s:gKTpfLbJFc4:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=qyYpFLerx5s:gKTpfLbJFc4:V_sGLiPBpWU"