(6924, 616, 'blockquote_list_1_blockquote_text', 'The Movie Metropolis will be the most advanced movie studio with the largest investment in the world. Wanda has invited the world’s leading companies and talent to develop this project. I believe that with its opening… it will become one of the major centers for global film.'),
