(7159, 619, '_intro_background_image', 'field_576bd0d0fd95b'),
(7160, 619, 'intro_title', 'Introduction'),
(7161, 619, '_intro_title', 'field_576bd0bbfd959'),
(7162, 619, 'intro_subtitle', 'The Centerpriece of the movie metropolis'),
(7163, 619, '_intro_subtitle', 'field_576bd0c4fd95a'),
(7164, 619, 'intro_text_1', '<strong>Wanda Studios will be the first and only world-class filmmaking destination in China meeting international standards.</strong> It will feature <strong>30 purpose-built soundstages, among which will be the world’s largest at 10,000 m<sup>2</sup>.</strong> It will also offer the <strong>largest exterior water tank in China</strong>, and the country’s most advanced temperature-controlled underwater stage.'),
(7165, 619, '_intro_text_1', 'field_576bd0defd95c'),
(7166, 619, 'intro_text_2', '<strong>Atop technologically advanced and Hollywood endorsed facilities</strong>, Wanda Studios will establish a comprehensive, first-class production services unit, a one-stop-shop helping with permits, banking needs, production needs and so much more to navigate China and Qingdao - all to ensure <strong>filming at the studios will be as easy and efficient as possible</strong>.\r\n\r\n<strong>The city of Qingdao is an optimum shooting location</strong>: a bustling port, offering a garden-like studio background embraced by mountains, rivers, reservoir and wetland. The city of Qingdao and Wanda Studios will jointly offer a competitive production incentive and cash rebate program - the first of its kind in China - with details to be unveiled November 2016 in Los Angeles.'),
(7167, 619, '_intro_text_2', 'field_576bd0edfd95d'),
