(7328, 664, '_climate_title', 'field_577114f37dcae'),
(7329, 664, 'climate_content', 'Qingdao features a continental climate with four distinct seasons. While the spring and fall display beautiful scenes of nature and a mild climate, winter is generally cold and dry with frosty nights; and summer, hot and sultry.'),
