(8585, 687, 'surronund_content', 'Qingdao boasts historic European and modern Asian architecture, with scenic destinations of mountains, rivers, reservoirs and wetlands. It is home to the longest sea bridge that links Qingdao and Huangdao.\r\n\r\nHome to China’s most internationally well-known brewery, Tsingtao Beer, and to reputable, multinational consumer electronics and home appliances corporation, Haier.'),
