(9413, 750, 'description', 'International and Domestic Production Incentives Plus Tax Rebate Program for Registered Businesses\r\nPresented by:\r\nQingdao Movie Metropolis (QMM), Wanda Studios, Governments of Qingdao and Huangdao, and the West Coast Development Group'),
