(11971, 890, 'subtitle', 'With limitless options filming in or around water, <strong>Wanda Studios’ Marine Facilities destination boasts two state-of-the-art water tanks</strong>, among them Asia’s <strong>largest exterior tank</strong> coupled with Asia’s <strong>largest blue screen</strong>, as well as the only full-time underwater stage in the entire continent.'),
