(14759, 935, 'section_list_2_content', '<h3>Steel Workshop</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>“Flex” space – different uses to be determined by production needs</li>\r\n 	<li>Three phase and domestic power throughout the workshop space at a minimum\r\nof 10 x 32Amp and 10 x 16Amp cee form socket outlets; domestic power at 10m intervals</li>\r\n 	<li>Industrial sink with hot and cold water</li>\r\n 	<li>Standpipe with hose connection and mop wash sink</li>\r\n 	<li>Break room with kitchenette</li>\r\n 	<li>Plumbing and waste for white goods (in preparation for costumes use)</li>\r\n 	<li>Storage cages or securable rooms with adequate ventilation for storage or dangerous goods</li>\r\n</ul>'),
