(14803, 936, 'section_list_1_content', '<h3>Carpenter / Wood Mill</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Dust extraction, LEV (local exhaust ventilation), and sawdust collection in line with modern film construction needs</li>\r\n 	<li>All industrial power feature “emergency stops” at regular points on workshop walls</li>\r\n 	<li>Three phase and domestic power throughout the workshop space at a\r\nminimum of 10 x 32Amp and 10 x 16Amp cee form socket outlets; domestic power at 10m intervals</li>\r\n 	<li>Compressed air for pneumatic tools supplied around workshop periphery</li>\r\n 	<li>Roof truss RSJ with block and tackle and a designated safe working load</li>\r\n 	<li>Industrial sink with hot and cold water</li>\r\n 	<li>Overhead power via extension reels</li>\r\n 	<li>High-speed network connectivity</li>\r\n 	<li>Break room with kitchenette</li>\r\n 	<li>Storage cages or securable rooms with adequate ventilation for storage or dangerous goods</li>\r\n 	<li>Hand and eye wash stations</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Steel Workshop</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>LEV (local exhaust ventilation) provided for welding areas</li>\r\n 	<li>Roof truss RSJ with block and tackle and a designated safe working load</li>\r\n 	<li>Three phase and domestic power throughout the workshop space at a minimum\r\nof 10 x 32Amp and 10 x 16Amp cee form socket outlets; domestic power at 10m intervals</li>\r\n 	<li>Compressed air for pneumatic tools supplied around workshop periphery</li>\r\n 	<li>High-speed network connectivity</li>\r\n 	<li>Industrial sink with hot and cold water supply</li>\r\n 	<li>Break room with kitchenette</li>\r\n 	<li>Storage cages or securable rooms with adequate ventilation for storage or dangerous goods</li>\r\n 	<li>Gas storage cages</li>\r\n 	<li>Hand and eye wash stations</li>\r\n</ul>'),
