(14857, 937, 'blockquote_list_0_blockquote_text', '<strong>Chairman Wang Jianlin </strong> always had a dream: he wanted a Chinese Hollywood. He now scripts his Hollywood dreams, <strong>building the Movie Metropolis </strong> . It is the <strong>largest entertainment infrastructure project ever undertaken</strong>'),
